{"tid":2036502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好多家長都好有貨，入左獄既義士登記番，每位配對家長(s) 計番補償金","createTime":"2020-05-26T13:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T13:45:44.000Z","uid":771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"70fa737043d3a4b99a6d01458b392561916fcf4d","tid":2036502,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:29:52.000Z","msg":"坐一個月一萬<br />\n<br />\n有冇議員/區議員發起<br />\n<br />\n好簡單<br />\n<br />\n出左獄既手足想有補償金聯絡議員<br />\n<br />\n議員係channel 出post<br />\n<br />\n當坐左一年12個月，姐係要籌12萬<br />\n<br />\n夠家長(s) 認捐就幫佢地配對自己解決<br />\n<br />\n咁又唔怕d 錢集埋左一舊比狗充公<br />\n<br />\n之前星火果8000萬<br />\n<br />\n起馬夠800個手足補償一年坐監"},{"pid":"245fce8ddf868a6149c040f14cc4bb26dcb7d022","tid":2036502,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:31:03.000Z","msg":"我認捐直接配對手足十萬先<br />\n<br />\n與其打場唔會既贏既官司<br />\n<br />\n我寧願坐監手足一出黎果下唔洗憂半年衣食先"},{"pid":"a7c62f6b946e2704ac4eff54685e8925915ccb70","tid":2036502,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:33:09.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n開始有手足坐緊冤獄<br />\n<br />\n要好好補償番"},{"pid":"23b6a39698f22fc53f4e929a6c8b42448662a554","tid":2036502,"uid":771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"我當有30% 既手足有需要<br />\n<br />\n平均刑期係2年<br />\n<br />\n2000人定罪<br />\n<br />\n要大約total 1.8億補償金<br />\n<br />\n我個人黎睇<br />\n<br />\n舊錢好少野姐"},{"pid":"28fc39cb5f4a1f04804a43fb1d403d630c37b6dc","tid":2036502,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23b6a39698f22fc53f4e929a6c8b42448662a554","tid":2036502,"uid":771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"我當有30% 既手足有需要<br />\n<br />\n平均刑期係2年<br />\n<br />\n2000人定罪<br />\n<br />\n要大約total 1.8億補償金<br />\n<br />\n我個人黎睇<br />\n<br />\n舊錢好少野姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"好啊你比住先"},{"pid":"c25f43d776453c21aa6851a94273c9ff126585eb","tid":2036502,"uid":771,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"q